CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 7, 1957, pg. A6, reads: "Maps Carter Confab - In cooperation with the current program of the Urban League, Wesley Center Church will sponsor a Career Conference at the church Sept. 17 at 7:30 P. M. Members of the planning committee, seated, left to right, are Shirley Lucas, Ralston Lucas and Myota Hill.  Standing: Patricia Chavis, Vera Thompson, Shirley Baker, Sarah Churchill and Anne [Ann] Sharpe. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of career conference planning committee seated from left: Shirley Lucas, Ralston Lucas, Myota Hill; standing: Patricia Chavis, Vera Thompson (Matthews), Shirley Baker, Sarah Churchill, and Ann Sharpe Haley, posed in Wesley Center AME Zion Church
